♟️ Checkers vs AI (Python)
This is a Python-based checkers game where a human player competes against a basic AI opponent. The game includes a visual board rendered with pygame, and uses custom logic for moves, captures, and game state.

🔧 Features
Two-player checkers game (Player vs AI)

Simple AI that makes random or semi-strategic moves

Interactive board with piece dragging

Visual assets for black and white pieces

🧾 Files Included
File	Description
Checkers 24.py	Main game script (run this to play)
black.png	Black checker piece image
white.png	White checker piece image

▶️ How to Play
Ensure you have Python 3 installed.

Install pygame if you haven’t already:

bash
Copy
Edit
pip install pygame
Run the game:

bash
Copy
Edit
python "Checkers 24.py"
Play as white; click and drag pieces to move.

